---
import MarketingLayout from '../../core/layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout title="Mukoko - African Community Platform | Nyuchi">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section bg-tech-abstract">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="hero-content text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Ubuntu Philosophy Badge -->
          <div class="badge-zw-yellow mb-8">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            Ubuntu Philosophy ‚Ä¢ Community First
          </div>

          <h1 class="heading-hero mb-8">
            Mukoko
            <br />
            <span class="text-gray-400">African Community Platform</span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Honoring the rich tradition of African community storytelling and shared knowledge, creating a unified entertainment platform where news, stories, and community conversations flow together like the great rivers of Africa.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-16">
            <a href="#platform" class="btn-marketing-primary">
              Explore Platform
            </a>
            <a href="#architecture" class="btn-marketing-secondary">
              Technical Details
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platform Overview -->
    <section id="platform" class="section-marketing">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="heading-section mb-6">
            5-Component Ecosystem
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            A comprehensive social media ecosystem celebrating African culture, storytelling, and community connection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Clips -->
          <div class="card-marketing">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl">üì∞</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Clips</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Curated news with AI-powered summaries and community discussion threads for meaningful engagement.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pulse -->
          <div class="card-marketing">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl">‚ö°</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pulse</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              TikTok-style trending content featuring breaking news, viral moments, and cultural celebrations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Connect -->
          <div class="card-marketing">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl">ü§ù</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Connect</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Social forum with "Circles" - interest-based communities fostering unity and mutual support.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Novels -->
          <div class="card-marketing">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl">üìö</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Novels</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Web novel platform supporting African authors worldwide, preserving and sharing our stories.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Events -->
          <div class="card-marketing lg:col-span-1 md:col-span-2 lg:col-start-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-2xl">üé™</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Events</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Centralized hub for community gatherings, cultural celebrations, and collaborative activities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Brand Values -->
    <section class="section-marketing bg-gray-900/30">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="heading-section mb-8">
            Ubuntu Philosophy
          </h2>
          
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <!-- Interconnected hexagonal logo representing community -->
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-2xl">üåç</span>
                African Excellence
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Success stories, innovation, and cultural celebrations showcasing the best of Africa.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-2xl">ü§ù</span>
                Community Connection
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Unity, mutual support, and collective action building stronger communities.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-2xl">üìö</span>
                Stories & Knowledge
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Literature, wisdom sharing, and honoring our storytelling traditions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technical Architecture -->
    <section id="architecture" class="section-marketing bg-tech-circuit">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="heading-section mb-6">
            Enterprise-Grade Architecture
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Built for scale with mobile-first design optimized for African smartphone users.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-800">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Mobile-First Tech Stack</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">React Native + Expo (native performance)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Go backend (4x faster than Node.js)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Cloudflare Workers (sub-10ms latency)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Base blockchain (low-cost Web3)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">ScyllaDB (10-100x faster queries)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="card-marketing">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Performance Metrics</h4>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-400">Global latency</span>
                  <span class="text-white font-medium">8-12ms</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-400">Scalability</span>
                  <span class="text-white font-medium">1M+ users</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-400">Cost efficiency</span>
                  <span class="text-white font-medium">$0.008/user/month</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-400">App startup</span>
                  <span class="text-white font-medium">1.2s</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-marketing">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Key Differentiators</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">‚úì</span>
                  <span>Mobile-first design for African smartphone users</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">‚úì</span>
                  <span>Low-latency edge computing across the continent</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">‚úì</span>
                  <span>Cultural authenticity built with Ubuntu values</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">‚úì</span>
                  <span>Web3 integration with affordable transaction fees</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project Status -->
    <section class="section-marketing bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-purple-900/20">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="badge-zw-green mb-8">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full animate-pulse mr-2"></div>
            Beta Launch Ready
          </div>

          <h2 class="heading-section mb-8">
            Ready for African Market
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
            Multi-component ecosystem deployed with enterprise-grade architecture, optimized for African users and built on Ubuntu philosophy of community connection.
          </p>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="card-marketing text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">5</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400">Platform Components</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-marketing text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">1M+</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400">User Capacity</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-marketing text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">8ms</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400">Average Latency</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-marketing text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">54</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400">African Countries</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section-marketing">
      <div class="container-marketing">
        <div class="cta-card max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="heading-section mb-6">
            Experience Ubuntu in Technology
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Join us in building the future of African community platforms. Where technology meets tradition, and innovation honors our heritage.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/marketing/contact" class="btn-marketing-primary">
              Partner With Us
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:hello@nyuchi.com" class="btn-marketing-secondary">
              Learn More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>